{
  "text": "When we got our introduction back from our publisher to the book which was originally called The Law Of One, in the introduction Carla had been speaking of reincarnation and there was a sentence added. It said, \"For although originally part of Jesus' teachings they were censored from all subsequent editions by the Empress. \" Would Ra please comment on the source of that being placed in our introduction? I am Ra. This follows the way of subjectively interesting happenings, conditions, circumstances, or coincidences. We would suggest one more full query at this time.",
